Package: RiskParityBrazil
Title: An analysis of risk parity applied to the Brazilian stock market
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Giuseppe",
           family = "Tomio",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "g.tinti.tomio@gmail.com")
Description: A complete pipeline that downloads financial data, simulates
    the historical performance of risk parity portfolios in the Brazilian
    stock market and presents the results in monthly updated dashboards
    along with a web article. Implemented as a R package on top of the R
    package targets (pipeline management). Deployed with GitHub Pages.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/GiuseppeTT/RiskParityBrazil,
    https://giuseppett.github.io/RiskParityBrazil/
